  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Randomized controlled trial comparing between two technique of laparoscopic sleeve
      gastrectomy for treatment of morbid obesity. In the first technique the investigators
      started dissection of gastrocolic ligament 6 cm from pylorus and in the second one the
      distance was only 2 cm. The main primary outcome measure was weight loss.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
